00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:55,600
Tapi ayah awak sembuh. Maksud saya…

253
00:15:55,680 --> 00:15:57,080
Dia tak cedera teruk.

254
00:15:57,160 --> 00:15:59,280
- Masuk hospital beberapa minggu.
- Okey.

255
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:01,680
Tapi di hospital, dia dijangkiti MRSA.

256
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:04,880
Jangkitan itu bunuh dia.

257
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:09,480
Jadi, bagi ibu saya,
Iain Adair bunuh ayah saya juga.

258
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:10,440
Itulah…

