- Awak serius?

275
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:20,600
- Ya.
- Tapi kita jumpa orang telur Rabu ini.

276
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:23,320
Lupakan dia. Maafkan saya. Tolonglah.

277
00:17:23,840 --> 00:17:24,680
Tolonglah!

278
