417
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:28,920
Orang gila. Psiko celaka bertaraf Olimpik.

418
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:39,840
Ibu cuma fikir,
kalau kamu lama lagi di sini,

419
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:41,760
