Di kurungan
Diseksa penuh sadis

527
00:33:36,560 --> 00:33:38,120
Di kurungan

528
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:40,160
Kau melutut dan menangis

529
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,640
Di kurungan

