Ya, Kenny.

600
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:15,800
Masuklah, Janet.

601
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:47,800
Pai kotej.

602
00:40:51,360 --> 00:40:53,640
Pai kotej. Dah siap.

603
00:40:57,600 --> 00:40:58,720
Okey.

604
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,520
Mak cik akan sajikan.

605
