Datang sini sekarang!

627
00:44:29,760 --> 00:44:31,800
Mak cik takkan apa-apakan awak!

628
00:45:01,960 --> 00:45:02,800
Tidak.

629
00:45:05,160 --> 00:45:06,240
Celaka!

630
00:45:08,280 --> 00:45:09,440
Sial!

631
00:45:09,920 --> 00:45:12,480
Celaka!

632
00:45:13,320 --> 00:45:17,720
Sial! Celaka! Sial!

633
