649
00:48:53,160 --> 00:48:54,480
Permainan seks.

650
00:48:55,360 --> 00:48:56,480
Saya dah kahwin.

651
00:48:56,560 --> 00:48:59,240
Kelakuan mereka malam itu, pengalaman itu,

652
00:48:59,880 --> 00:49:02,840
