689
00:51:14,640 --> 00:51:16,080
Buat lawak sekarang.

690
00:51:17,160 --> 00:51:18,600
Alamak, dia datang.

691
00:51:19,760 --> 00:51:22,280
Saya cuma nak cakap, saya minat awak.

692
00:51:22,360 --> 00:51:24,360
Rancangan awak sangat bagus.

693
00:51:24,440 --> 00:51:25,960
Terima kasih.

694
00:51:26,040 --> 00:51:28,520
Awak lelaki Loch Henry itu?

695
